{"tid":2388203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Switch 下代或命名 Super Switch 配備 OLED 熒幕 + 4K 解像度","createTime":"2021-01-31T02:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T05:43:54.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea84272545dd2b7269e2ebd9cdf843e12a924b7","tid":2388203,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/https___hk.hypebeast.com_files_2020_04_https___hk.hypebeast.com_files_2019_08_nintendo-switch-new-model-free-eligible-customers-0-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F01%2Fhttps___hk.hypebeast.com_files_2020_04_https___hk.hypebeast.com_files_2019_08_nintendo-switch-new-model-free-eligible-customers-0-1.jpg&h=10abc17b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任天堂遊戲主機 Nintendo Switch 已推出接近 4 年時間，外界一直有消息指任天堂將會為 Switch 推出後繼機款 Switch Pro。然而，根據最新消息指，新款 Switch 很可能會命名為 Super Switch，並會升級處理器，以及配備 OLED 熒幕和解像度等。<br />\n<br />\n根據外媒《WccfTech》引述巴西記者 PH Brazil 消息指，下一代 Switch 將會被命名為 Super Switch，與早前另一位在 Twitter 上的爆料者 @Tyler_McV 提及的名稱一致。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/Tyler_McV/status/1317096095659528192?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FTyler_McV%2Fstatus%2F1317096095659528192%3F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=bad7741f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2FTyler_McV%2Fstatus%2F1317096095659528192%3F&h=95abd654\" target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/Tyler_McV/status/1317096095659528192?</a><br />\n<br />\n而早前外國知名駭客 SciresM 也在 ResetERA 討論區上爆料，指新一代 Switch 比起上一代將會有顯著的升級，包括採用 OLED 熒幕、提供 4K 解像度、使用 Mariko SoC 特殊處理器等，而電池續航以及散熱系統也會有著不少提升。<br />\n<br />\n外界推測新一代 Nintendo Switch Pro 或會在 2021 年內推出，更有指任天堂會趕及在《MONSTER HUNTER RISE》推出前，即 3  月中旬推出新一代主機，有興趣的玩家或可拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2021/01/28/super-switch/game-channel/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2021%2F01%2F28%2Fsuper-switch%2Fgame-channel%2F%3F&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=5e679544\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2021/01/28/super-switch/game-channel/?</a>"},{"pid":"705a958af9113ff092fb5257cbcca183142e64a9","tid":2388203,"uid":278184,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"每幾個月就講一次會出新switch<br />\n講左幾年<br />\n最記得有次講到似層層<br />\n點似最後出左部lite<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95da8a12cff5b9a3ba37fa16523c716a8652a568","tid":2388203,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:08:58.000Z","msg":"Oled <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ea56dc4908de66361161d5192c2e3190664814b","tid":2388203,"uid":387466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:09:53.000Z","msg":"閃MON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5246db9d0ce009eeee19310c0179455d20609cef","tid":2388203,"uid":288304,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"705a958af9113ff092fb5257cbcca183142e64a9","tid":2388203,"uid":278184,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"每幾個月就講一次會出新switch<br />\n講左幾年<br />\n最記得有次講到似層層<br />\n點似最後出左部lite<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T03:19:57.000Z","ms